{"tid":992763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自己既路係咪一直都行錯咗？","createTime":"2019-01-23T11:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T12:56:32.000Z","uid":197024,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"403578022e5d088e57efb14d84ebdcae473c069a","tid":992763,"uid":197024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:58:31.000Z","msg":"一個想記錄下自己對生活，人生嘅感受嘅post。睇唔明係正常，因為我自己都唔係幾明呢幾年發生咗乜嘢事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tXu-4BcZfE0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtXu-4BcZfE0&d=aJoDg7%2FdIljMrna1Ylq5yBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=94ce6a40\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tXu-4BcZfE0</a><br />\n<br />\n喺美國讀書嘅時間，係我最開心嘅日子。<br />\n日子過得好充實，每日4點幾起身出去做gym,跟住返學。<br />\n又識得多fd,成日成班int'l student去玩。<br />\n感覺每一日都好有希望。<br />\n因為自己嘅一個理想，選擇咗transfer去日本。亦係我人生開始仆街嘅日子。<br />\n喺日本嗰兩年，除咗學識日文之外，嗰段日子一直唔想再回憶。<br />\n<br />\n真係一個令自己後悔嘅決定。<br />\n<br />\n返咗嚟香港之後，轉過兩份工，每一份都做唔長。感覺同呢個地方生活嘅人嘅mindset好唔同。<br />\n<br />\n自己一直好想返美國生活，但係一直都冇辦法。<br />\n<br />\n開始覺得自己好迷失。點解好似一直行錯路。<br />\n<br />\n已經行得好攰，再行落去嘅話好驚連自己僅餘嘅少少對以前開心嘅日子都會忘記。始終記憶係推動我往前行嘅動力。"},{"pid":"b464eaf4b7169ad972bed34dd88847185d1a2b2b","tid":992763,"uid":46835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"我當年攞咗h1b 做咗兩年幾嘢喺嗰邊<br />\n但係就返咗嚟HK<br />\n<br />\n而家後悔到仆街!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188d9266870ad6ca1b494d530203ef7652a7ff42","tid":992763,"uid":197024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b464eaf4b7169ad972bed34dd88847185d1a2b2b","tid":992763,"uid":46835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"我當年攞咗h1b 做咗兩年幾嘢喺嗰邊<br />\n但係就返咗嚟HK<br />\n<br />\n而家後悔到仆街!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"transfer去日本係一個好錯嘅決定。<br />\n<br />\n而家已經冇機會返去。"},{"pid":"60f95859920f8a8eb36b16092e983d6577530b6c","tid":992763,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:20:10.000Z","msg":"有冇mindset唔同既例子"},{"pid":"bd96d079cbcd65a0980eac027bf438b9878fba66","tid":992763,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:23:47.000Z","msg":"後生果陣 迷失的時候 我都會睇下steve jobs 果段 speech...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;You can't connect the dots looking forward; you can only connect them looking backwards. So you have to trust that the dots will somehow connect in your future. You have to trust in something &ndash; your gut, destiny, life, karma, whatever.<br />\n<br />\n睇你都仲後生...青春已經係本錢喇"},{"pid":"ec49c62b39c2599116e81511b522ae877e893504","tid":992763,"uid":75998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:26:55.000Z","msg":"仲有其他路嘅 發掘下啦 私心推薦澳洲 日子都過得好開心 未喺其他地方住過推介唔到其他<br />\n<br />\n香港只係一個中轉站 努力啲搵方法 好好裝備自己 時間成熟就跳走香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d704ebdc7e045c347542732b80c161b0fceab66","tid":992763,"uid":161098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"努力追個鬼妹結婚移民去美國囉，或者去做/讀有得技術移民嘅工種囉。<br />\n<br />\nbtw其實你未必係揀錯路導致冇希望，好多人都係讀書時滿懷希望，讀完出社會先知乜叫撲街，所以又唔使咁灰，好常見嘅經歷來，唸下其他路搵多個目標啦。"},{"pid":"2edf74d633d8ac8bdce06bfe80fbf10daa4b3166","tid":992763,"uid":197024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60f95859920f8a8eb36b16092e983d6577530b6c","tid":992763,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:20:10.000Z","msg":"有冇mindset唔同既例子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:56:32.000Z","msg":"正確啲嚟講，係對呢個地方嘅人同事冇乜嘢投入感。"}]}